<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #4F46E5, #9333EA);
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #4F46E5, #9333EA);
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to The Gross Profit Podcast!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @name %>,</h2>
        <p>Thank you for subscribing to The Gross Profit Podcast! We're excited to have you join our community of finance professionals and business leaders.</p>
        
        <p>Our podcast explores financial strategies that drive business success through conversations with leading CFOs, finance experts, and business leaders.</p>
        
        <p>Stay tuned for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>In-depth conversations with finance leaders</li>
          <li>Practical advice for business growth</li>
          <li>Insights on financial strategy and metrics</li>
          <li>Stories from successful entrepreneurs and CFOs</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Visit our website to explore our latest episodes:</p>
        <a href="<%= @url %>" class="button">Visit The Gross Profit Podcast</a>
        
        <p>We'll notify you when new episodes are released.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The Gross Profit Podcast Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> The Gross Profit Podcast. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>If you received this email by mistake, please ignore it or <a href="mailto:podcast@procurementexpress.com">contact us</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>